div.p:
"You're here, Doctor;
                            aren't you?" asked the slow, curly-wigged brother, squatting
                        himself on the grass.

"Will you mind your own business, and go to sleep ?"
                        said Tommy. "I am going;
                            I said I should."

" There she comes," said his wife, looking out of
                        the window, " by the garden gate, with a great basket;
                            what has she been after ?"
